name: Roy Tang
text: hindi naman kasi necesarilly curbstomp ang situation. more of may averaging kasi ng skill levels so even if a single team member in a five man team is suddenly 5% less efficient, the team only takes a 1% drop in efficiency (conversely, extra efficiency is equally distributed as well)
